    <para>
      First, make several changes that are required for Valgrind to function on
      systems with glibc-2.43 and Linux 6.18.x installed:
    </para>

<screen><userinput remap="pre">patch -Np1 -i ../valgrind-&valgrind-version;-upstream_fixes-1.patch</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Next, regenerate the build system since we adjusted the Makefiles:
    </para>

<screen><userinput remap="pre">autoreconf -fiv</userinput></screen>
